Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.71,0:01:45.96,Background,,0,0,0,,Or is Internet Go mere fun\Nand games for Touya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.72,0:01:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but there are games that I can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:58.43,Sai,,0,0,0,,I knew that he would walk the same path\Nas I do, ever since I first met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:02.99,Sai,,0,0,0,,The same path to master the divine move...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:06.92,Sai,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow! My wish will be granted!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:10.11,Sai,,0,0,0,,How much closer can I get...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:12.03,Sai,,0,0,0,,to the divine move!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.95,0:02:18.95,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(315,115)}The Fifty-Fifth Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:23.96,Background,,0,0,0,,How long will that study session last, Akira-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Until late afternoon, probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you'll be eating dinner at home, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, what about the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:38.94,Background,,0,0,0,,Your father told me not to go today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.10,0:02:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to go!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to play Go on the Internet\Nwithout intrusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's leaving the hospital tomorrow. He\Nshould take this chance to rest up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:55.94,Background,,0,0,0,,Why is Go the only thing that\Neither of you think about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll be going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:08.47,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Wow, he's getting out tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.47,0:03:13.49,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I was really worried when he collapsed ten days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:21.64,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to play Shindou on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:27.31,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The next chance I'll have to play him will\Nbe during the Wakajishisen, next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:33.99,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But I can watch Shindou's matches against\Nother pro players before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:37.82,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll measure Shindou's strength from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:44.99,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Yes... It won't be too long now...\Nuntil I find out exactly who he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:48.54,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs31.5\1c&H55332E&\bord0\pos(389,53)\frx0\fry6}N\NO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:48.54,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs31.5\1c&H55332E&\bord0\pos(389,152)\frx0\fry6}V\NI\NS\NI\NT\NO\NR\NS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:04:00.30,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But for my father to want to play Internet\NGo, without being interrupted?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:02.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He certainly seems absorbed in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:05.81,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He didn't seem to like it very much when he started.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:19.33,Sai,,0,0,0,,Finally, this day has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:31.97,Thinking,,0,0,0,,She's not Mitani's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:36.30,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's her day off. Or maybe she quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use this machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:47.54,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Master Touya is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:54.42,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But... is he serious about retiring if he loses?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:05:00.66,Memory,,0,0,0,,If I were to lose, I will retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:03.19,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's probably serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:08.05,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Man, why is that family so stubborn!?
