Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:42.28,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I don't care if he has to retire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:46.14,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I get to watch this match from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:50.43,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I get to watch this match between Sai and Touya Meijin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:44.74,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:49.45,Background,,0,0,0,,Yoshitaka! What were you out all night!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:52.79,Background,,0,0,0,,I thought the tutoring game was\Nsupposed to end last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I played Go at Saeki-san's place, and stayed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:08:01.51,Background,,0,0,0,,I told you to call home whenever you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:04.21,Background,,0,0,0,,I tried to call your cell, but you had turned it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:07.52,Background,,0,0,0,,Breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I had it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:14.93,Background,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll get my own place, just like Saeki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get more referrals from the Master,\Nand pick up more record keeper jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have the money from my matches, too.\NI should be able to pay for my own room...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about food and laundry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll try playing on the net for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:44.65,Background,,0,0,0,,Yoshitaka, are you going to be home today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:47.30,Background,,0,0,0,,You're eating lunch and dinner at home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'll have them at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be the fake Sai from before.\NHe showed up again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it a different fake Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:04.45,Background,,0,0,0,,toya... koyo...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? Touya Kouyou!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a fake Touya Meijin, too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that the Meijin\Nwould play Go on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the type that looks down on\Nit, just like Master Morishita.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, isn't he still in the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess he could play\Nif he had a private room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be him, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in a match. Who is he playing?
