Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be an incredible match\Nif they were the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:55.28,Computer,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HD8D8BD&}{\an7\pos(0,0)}{\p1}m 81 8 l 196 8 l 196 64 l 81 64 m 77 174 l 295 174 l 295 227 l 77 227 m 321 191 l 332 191 l 332 201 l 321 201 m 321 212 l 332 212 l 332 224 l 321 224 m 428 177 l 545 177 l 545 227 l 428 227 m 72 282 l 296 282 l 296 334 l 72 334 m 348 277 l 583 277 l 583 333 l 348 333 m 73 405 l 306 405 l 306 461 l 73 461{\p0}
