Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:55.28,Computer,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H2E260E&\an7\fnArial\fs56\blur2\fscy110\pos(84,175)}Captured: 0 Stones
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:55.28,Computer,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H2E260E&\an7\fnArial\fs56\blur2\fscy110\pos(84,277)}Rem.Time: 165 / 180
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:55.28,Computer,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H2E260E&\an7\fnArial\fs44\blur2\fscy110\pos(86,412)}MATCH INFO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? They have three hours!? On the net!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be.... the Meijin!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the real Sai!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Meneer Ooijer. Thanks for the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And why are you calling me\Nat this time of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:10:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Touya Kouyou is playing on the net?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And who is he playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Sai. The person you told\Nme about the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if he's the real thing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai, you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:21.20,Background,,0,0,0,,Playing Touya Kouyou!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:23.33,Background,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's around noon in Japan right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya Kouyou and... Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.20,Thinking,,0,0,0,,So this is Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:07.33,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.75,Thinking,,0,0,0,,a worthy opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:21.64,Background,,0,0,0,,See, it's Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! And he's playing Toya Koyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here because I wanted\Nto watch them play together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the clock, they have three hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.36,0:12:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! This is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:38.32,Background,,0,0,0,,I'll go make some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:40.58,Background,,0,0,0,,Yeah, make some for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is incredible, is it really that Sai!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:54.38,Background,,0,0,0,,The Sai who disappeared from the net\Nafter the match against Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's an incredible match.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai vs. toya koyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The match has progressed peacefully so\Nfar. I wonder how it'll go from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:17.94,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's not just an amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:24.17,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But he doesn't remind me of any pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:35.00,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I have no intentions of taking back my\Nword that I will retire if I lose, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:43.59,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If I win...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:46.56,Thinking,,0,0,0,,You have to tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:51.73,Thinking,,0,0,0,,who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:58.07,Background,,0,0,0,,What a surprise, Sai is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's playing Toya Koyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I played Toya Koyo before, he's Touya Meijin\Nfrom Japan. There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai is playing the Meijin evenly,\Ntoo. He's definitely the Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.56,Background,,0,0,0,,from two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:50.87,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:16.40,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I see what he's trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.13,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya made a move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this what White....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:15:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,what Sai wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the answer that the Meijin\Ncame up with after all that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:30.51,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This should be exactly what you wanted. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:38.69,Thinking,,0,0,0,,by cautiously attacking from the Boushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:44.11,Thinking,,0,0,0,,the situation turns into one that's not bad at all for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:50.91,Background,,0,0,0,,It's Touya Meijin! It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I had no idea things could turn out this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:59.84,Background,,0,0,0,,It looked as if Sai had the advantage...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:01.98,Background,,0,0,0,,But now that we're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:05.75,Background,,0,0,0,,That first move that Sai made... it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:09.93,Background,,0,0,0,,It's lost its meaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! You're awesome, Master Touya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my Go. The Go of the Meijin, Touya Kouyou!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.76,0:17:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't hold back. I will win and\Nmake you name yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:40.71,Background,,0,0,0,,Touya Meijin was okay this time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.88,Background,,0,0,0,,he has a full schedule of matches
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,outside the country next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be surprised if he collapses again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we young ones have\Nto take on a title or two from him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to lighten his load a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogata-san is doing well in the Jyudan\Nmatch with two wins and two losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And Kurata has finally gotten the challenger\Nspot for the next Honinbou match.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to keep moving, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Touya-kun, you're here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I invited him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He comes up with all these great moves.\NWe've been learning from him all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Master Touya's health? Is he okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.01,0:18:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you see the fourth game of the Jyudan\Nmatch? He's healthier than you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be leaving the hospital in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's playing on the Internet right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Internet? Master Touya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, he doesn't look like the type.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:46.02,Background,,0,0,0,,Are they playing right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:48.40,Background,,0,0,0,,You have a PC. Turn it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't play on the Internet much, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what do you use your PC for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useful for organizing records of games.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his handle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,His real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:03.54,Background,,0,0,0,,Touya...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Internet Go... maybe I'll get a PC, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is, toya koyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.28,0:19:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where? Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of spectators.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He is Touya Kouyou.
