Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:19.64,Background,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is incredible. What's going\Non with white on the top side?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The lower left looks interesting, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The game is... I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I can't tell how the game went.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,White isn't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Touya is black. He's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but white is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's an even game. He's playing\Nthis well in an even game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! They have three hours on the clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.09,0:19:51.66,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Yes. This is not just any player.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.55,Background,,0,0,0,,Exactly who is he playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:54.97,Background,,0,0,0,,Let's see....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.69,0:19:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,His opponent's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well you can't know, but he has to be a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:26.12,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:32.13,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This is Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:33.84,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's Sai!
