Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.16,0:22:18.50,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fad(334,334)}Fuseki is the opening of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:18.84,Background,,0,0,0,,White just went to 3,3 and here's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.18,0:22:25.56,Background,,0,0,0,,Should black go here, or go here? Which is better?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.22,0:22:29.44,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs22.5\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(626,459)\frx70\t(0,542,1,\frx0)\3c&H008708&\4c&H008708&\fscx100\fscy100\bord1\shad0.5\pos(328,381)}Which side is it better to                          play from{\i1}?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.87,0:22:30.27,Background,,0,0,0,,Your hint is that black is trying\Nto gain territory on this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.97,0:22:35.78,Background,,0,0,0,,If black blocks off from this side,\Nthe game will progress like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:39.72,Background,,0,0,0,,And he gets a lot of territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.78,0:22:45.85,Background,,0,0,0,,If black blocks from the other\Nside, it will progress like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:50.18,Background,,0,0,0,,and we have no idea where\Nblack can make territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.13,0:22:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is a situation in which you\Nwant to block from this side.
