Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.94,0:23:01.53,Thinking,,0,0,0,,My father arranged to play against Sai ahead of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:03.95,Thinking,,0,0,0,,My father knows who Sai is!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.03,0:23:07.49,Background,,0,0,0,,They're both neck and neck now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.63,0:23:10.32,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He can play this well against Touya Kouyou,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:12.37,Thinking,,0,0,0,,yet we know nothing about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.76,0:23:26.30,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's the old Shindou that I see in Sai!
